Package com.mycompany.anothercam.StudentApplicationManager

Class StudentCampUnregister

java.lang.Object
com.mycompany.anothercam.StudentApplicationManager.StudentCampUnregister
public class StudentCampUnregister extends Object
Represents the StudentCampUnregister Object and the following assistance methods. A StudentCampUnregister is ran dependent on how many users are going to unregister for the camp.
